  "_readme": [
    "EDIT THIS FILE when the squad changes. The app reads it on load.",
    "",
    "A player LEAVES  → delete his object, or set \"gone\": true (keeps the record but",
    "                   removes him from the squad and the cost calculation).",
    "A player ARRIVES → add an object. amort = fee ÷ years. For a buy-back, amort runs",
    "                   on the NET of the two deals (Stankovic: paid 23, had received 10,",
    "                   so 13 on the books ÷ 5 years = 2.6).",
    "",
    "salary  = GROSS €/yr (this is what the cap counts; Capology reports gross)",
    "mult    = gross/net ratio, for the net display. ~1.5 with the Growth Decree, else ~1.84",
    "amort   = annual amortisation in €",
    "until   = contract expiry year",
    "spot    = starting XI slot: GK RCB CB LCB RWB LWB RM CM DM LM ST1 ST2. Omit for a backup.",
    "tier    = \"u23\" or \"primavera\" — kept off the pitch, and off the cost cap, but sellable",
    "",
    "cash    = the summer ledger. Add a line for every completed deal.",
    "talk    = optional transfer chatter shown when you tap a player."
